{"tid":293006,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原創音樂】《小智慧》- 關懷智障人仕主題音樂創作比賽季軍","createTime":"2017-06-21T22:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T16:19:14.000Z","uid":43264,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"203a524400103a8969566415e115811071cc094c","tid":293006,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:29:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dirYXsHEOVQ&amp;t=69s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdirYXsHEOVQ%26t%3D69s&d=I3RX4Vt7e7%2BDDS8qeelyHqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=d8ac1270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dirYXsHEOVQ&amp;t=69s</a><br />\n<br />\n這世界充滿了各種各樣的「尺」，以不同的標準，把人分類、分等級、分成「正常」和「不正常」。<br />\n<br />\n是的，也許這些標準有它們的存在意義。但我們卻逐漸地，把某些標準當成批判別人的唯一依據，希望用相同的尺，把所有人變成相同的模樣。<br />\n<br />\n世上總有些人未能勝過各種批判的目光，他們的想法也不一定能讓其他人完全理解。幸而，他們卻天生擁有不一樣的恩賜，能用不同的角度觀察世界。我相信，這反而是一種更難能可貴的智慧，一種不用跟旁人比拼的智慧。<br />\n<br />\n這種智慧，就是一種不需猜算的《小智慧》。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《小智慧》<br />\n作曲：Jason Ng<br />\n作詞：Rasaid Tsang<br />\n<br />\n月亮在天空對我笑 我心高興透了<br />\n你當做傻事 但我這刻的心意<br />\n怎麼給你知曉<br />\n<br />\n烈日在天花轉呀轉 照出光線暖暖<br />\n我已被熔掉 直到關燈的一秒<br />\n我願吻你的臉<br />\n<br />\n當天下事情難細說 多少的傷痛難治癒<br />\n卻有一顆愛的星光 仍然尚留在我心某處<br />\n<br />\n不必像別人能計算 誰懼怕給過路人論斷<br />\n再美麗動人 再智力滿分 都有盡處<br />\n<br />\n你機智他聰敏 我善良愛別人<br />\n這種最簡單的睿智可使我更吸引<br />\n有種聰慧 超出世間的智慧<br />\n才能讓愛亮遍天際<br />\n<br />\n你優雅他英偉 還是純真可貴<br />\n我可以不必猜度衷心相信這一切<br />\n願這世間 忘懷各種心計<br />\n重頭學會 不需精算 這種聰慧<br />\n<br />\n這算愚或智不太重要 盡力讓愛念蔓延<br />\n幸福不靠數字來計算 才完美點<br />\n<br />\n不必問月兒圓與缺 不必於思緒裡翻轉<br />\n智慧若用完 我會用愛心 給你贈暖<br />\n<br />\n你機智他聰敏 我善良愛別人<br />\n這種最簡單的睿智可使我更吸引<br />\n有種聰慧 超出世間的智慧<br />\n才能讓愛亮遍天際<br />\n<br />\n你優雅他英偉 還是純真可貴<br />\n我可以不必猜度衷心相信這一切<br />\n願這世間 忘懷各種挑戰問題<br />\n從不需猜算 這種智慧<br />\n<br />\n我信每一種愛 能聯繫世間的一切<br />\n跨出天際"},{"pid":"255fa48e79aa90e75d1941989592b83322c0e77b","tid":293006,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:12:36.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e30c0854418babe617348daac4c4016487c83a2","tid":293006,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"點解會負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de37756fc088ac9baca57a84abffcb8697dee649","tid":293006,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354a644d1e54b48f86c27f0cf68514d3d63f4397","tid":293006,"uid":69247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推"},{"pid":"9e2b0e2d7715c74777d83adcf55e1d9b68f3775d","tid":293006,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推</blockquote><br />\n多謝火土巴打!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eb13d5dae7e17c7350e50ecfd931edbfbff79d","tid":293006,"uid":29724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"睇錯小智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f35637a56f6f77e09bc28ee482f63987e2d6990","tid":293006,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:17:26.000Z","msg":"貼返條link會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30bf0dfa22a5987891307c0c7507851cd17b515","tid":293006,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dirYXsHEOVQ&amp;